```

## Database Schema (Drizzle + Neon PostgreSQL)
Key tables:
- `locations` — Ås, Vestby, Drøbak branches with phone/address
- `categories` — Kebab, Grill, Salater, Barnemeny, Pizza, Tilbehør, Drikke
- `menu_items` — name, description, base_price, category_id, location_id, image_url, allergens
- `item_variants` — size options (Liten/Medium/Stor) with price delta
- `item_modifiers` — Sauce choice (Mild/Medium/Sterk/Uten saus), extras, removals
- `orders` — status (pending/confirmed/preparing/ready/delivered), location_id, total, delivery_type
- `order_items` — order_id, item_id, quantity, chosen modifiers, line_price
- `customers` — name, phone, email, address

## Business Logic Rules
1. Each location has its own menu (some items may differ between branches)
2. Customer must select a location before seeing the menu
3. Cart is location-scoped — switching location clears the cart (show confirmation dialog)
4. Sauce selection is OBLIGATORISK (required) on kebab items — block "Add to cart" until selected
5. Discount codes are validated server-side only — never trust client
6. Order confirmation sends SMS via Twilio to the customer's phone number
7. Admin panel polls for new orders every 30 seconds (or use Supabase Realtime / SSE)
8. Supported delivery types: "Henting" (pickup) and "Levering" (delivery, location-dependent)

## Norwegian Language
All customer-facing UI text must be in Norwegian (Bokmål):
- "Velg" = Select
- "Send inn ordre" = Place order
- "Din ordre" = Your order
- "Tøm handlekurv" = Clear cart
- "Tilbake" = Back
- "Neste" = Next
- "Totalt" = Total
- "Obligatorisk" = Required
- "Legg inn rabattkode" = Enter discount code

## Code Quality
- All components must be TypeScript strict
- Use server components by default; add `"use client"` only when needed (interactivity, hooks)
- API routes must validate input with Zod
- Never expose DB credentials — use environment variables only
- Loading states: skeleton loaders on menu grid, spinner on cart submit
- Error boundaries on menu and checkout pages

## Environment Variables Required
```
DATABASE_URL=          # Neon connection string
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=
NEXTAUTH_URL=
VIPPS_CLIENT_ID=
VIPPS_CLIENT_SECRET=
VIPPS_MERCHANT_SERIAL=
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=
```
